  "help": [
    {
      "textLabel": "One of the most important assets you have is the ability to work and earn an income. Disability insurance replace a portion of your income if you become sick or injured and are unable to work. This type of insurance is available available through both public and private programs. As a starting point, this tool helps you estimate the amount and duration of disability insurance needed for your specific situation. For further information, please consult an insurance professional."
